# .lociignore: what the palace audit and structural scans skip.
#
# A palace holds MEMORY (soul, handovers, crystals, tracker, CLAUDE.md, garden,
# rooms) and MATERIAL (vendored code, reference dumps, binaries the work
# consumes). Scans walk memory, not material. One glob per line.
# Copy this to your palace root and edit for your palace.

# Dependency / vendored trees
**/node_modules/**
**/.venv/**
**/venv/**
**/target/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**

# Reference dumps and source material the work consumes (rename to your layout)
material/**
reference/**
vendor/**
**/_sources/**

# Large binaries / non-prose
**/*.pdf
**/*.zip
**/*.gz
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.mp4

# OS noise
**/.DS_Store
